title: Mortal Kombat Project Double Up: 4.7 RAR & Anthology
description:
Mortal Kombat Project The Anthology 

By Indrid Cold & Co. 
This a must have for all MK Fans who can't wait for the MK vs DC Release! 

Get it while i'm seeding it cuz when i stop 
its a wrap. only other place is rapid share 
and you know how slow that is. lol 
It's the complete version with the debug mode WinMugen app of it with it all updates and shit. with all the characters that you'll need and even some open slots to add more characters! So have fun. 

With it you'll get the PrisT release of 4.7 with it!

Just unpack it, then go into the mkanthology folder and get the RAR/ZIP file with MKP 4.7 in it.
